<varlistentry id="options.Decoration">
	<term>Decoration <emphasis remap='I'>param1[,param2[,...]]</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Allows you to decorate your pager to your liking.
		The following parameters can be specified : NoDeskLabel, NoPageSeparator,
		NoSelection, SelectionColor, GridColor, DeskBorderWidth, DeskBorderColor,
		LabelBelowDesk, HideInactiveLabels, VerticalLabel.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="PagerDecorations#synopsis">Pager Decoration options</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
